snippet.title: Vigor – Official Release Trailer 🔪🍅
snippet.description:
Vigor has gone 1.0 and is now Free to Play for all players on Xbox One. 

The Update 1.0 - Rise includes: 
New Weapons

Story Challenges Extended

New Customization Variants

Starter Pack
Outlander Pack

Localization:English, French, Italian, German, Spanish, and Brazilian Portuguese

New Game Servers
